text: Sybra elongatissima is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1939. It is known from Borneo and Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Sybra elongatissima. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== elongatissima Category:Beetles described in 1939
title: Sybra elongatissima
